Hey!
 
Hope you're doing great. ð
 
I'm super excited to let you know about something special we've been cooking up. We're launching Platform in Glasgow, and I'd love for you to be part of the big night.
 
When: April 18th, 2024, from 6:30pm to 11pm
Where: Platform, right under those cool Victorian railway arches in Glasgow
 
We're calling it People Make Platform. It's going to be a mix of art, tunes, tasty bites, and drinks - all celebrating what makes Glasgow amazing. It's also a chance to meet other folks in the industry and chat about what's next for events in our city.
 
If this sounds like your kind of evening, could you drop me an email at jenna@camm-hooper.co.uk with your name and how many guests you're bringing? I'll get your RSVP sorted.
 
I really hope to see you there!
